{"tid":1980684,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣十八線歌手MV抄襲IU 支那網民:“有事就中国人，没事就台湾人”","createTime":"2020-04-20T08:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T09:42:54.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"590452d6368cb31d0db7c1b1221b0486eac176b2","tid":1980684,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T08:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2020-04-20/126070-833140.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2020-04-20%2F126070-833140.jpg&h=127d2574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這次擔任荳荳歌曲製作人跟導演的陳大天出面致歉，IU 的導演也出面回應此事，大家看完覺得如何呢？<br />\n<br />\n藝人荳荳推出新歌《可不可愛》，由知名藝人陳大天、呂策執導，還邀請到狼人殺偶像陳零九 feat 合作，但 MV 一推出便引發大批網友指出疑似抄襲 IU《Palette》的 MV。<br />\n<br />\n▼目前也在韓國論壇上也引發爭議，還整理出了相似的內容，比對兩支 MV 畫面。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n▼IU《Palette》MV：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d9IxdwEFk1c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dd9IxdwEFk1c&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPqZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=c8653459\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d9IxdwEFk1c</a><br />\n▼荳荳《可不可愛》MV： <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H6P76hYY_Ws\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DH6P76hYY_Ws&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPqZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=53d7f2ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H6P76hYY_Ws</a><br />\n▼《Palette》的李來慶（이래경音譯）導演也分享了此內容，並回應道：「最近收到了很多剽竊MV的舉報，因為這種事情很久以前就一直存在著，所以也漸漸地麻痺了。觀看MV的人知道它是抄襲的，那對我來說就足夠了，謝謝各位的所有舉報、應援和關心。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_dd80d2806a8a2ab821178e3f89001a7f/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-04-20/126070-833150.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_dd80d2806a8a2ab821178e3f89001a7f%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-04-20%2F126070-833150.jpg&h=58943040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_967c6c9b6cac32d57c92fe9bb2fc4a77/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-04-20/126070-833153.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_967c6c9b6cac32d57c92fe9bb2fc4a77%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-04-20%2F126070-833153.jpg&h=8da2e6e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼導演回應網友內容：「如你所知，他抄襲來的MV非常俗氣、質感低。他現在一定很尷尬。我很好。但我為他作為創作者感到遺憾。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_39bcfd87382b989c1696a748b28ff6ba/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-04-20/126070-833154.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_39bcfd87382b989c1696a748b28ff6ba%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-04-20%2F126070-833154.png&h=cfe969aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼陳大天開會時，的確也放了 IU 的 MV 做為參考，但目前被網友抨擊為「過度參考」了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_9cfe3fdb41c8269b6f70e70e0e81c351/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-04-20/126070-833157.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_9cfe3fdb41c8269b6f70e70e0e81c351%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-04-20%2F126070-833157.png&h=653497bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼隨後，陳大天也在《可不可愛》的 MV 下長文回應此事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_295acf14ab7efcf0e2558e04532f579c/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-04-20/126070-833162.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_295acf14ab7efcf0e2558e04532f579c%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-04-20%2F126070-833162.png&h=9ff8a7fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼荳荳回應網友。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_8f89803a13de358f50a928f970061865/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-04-20/126070-833164.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_8f89803a13de358f50a928f970061865%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-04-20%2F126070-833164.png&h=c9bb373f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/mw690/0067sxldgy1ge08532rntj30u20u0k9h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx2.sinaimg.cn%2Fmw690%2F0067sxldgy1ge08532rntj30u20u0k9h.jpg&h=96a58a52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p7e92XH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp7e92XH.png&h=0464e246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qgvJnXJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqgvJnXJ.png&h=6daa5e04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FSYZFKo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFSYZFKo.png&h=d873e629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vTzuiv4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvTzuiv4.png&h=1d794694&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mPsS0Kq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmPsS0Kq.png&h=fcc81208&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b58fe439c97c25f871428b1020239dbf01244c04","tid":1980684,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T08:54:39.000Z","msg":"Ok bye"},{"pid":"8ab2969616a2789857ff061d3906ef9c94fd2e75","tid":1980684,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b58fe439c97c25f871428b1020239dbf01244c04","tid":1980684,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T08:54:39.000Z","msg":"Ok bye"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T08:59:44.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"6a095e2c559dae67ac2e5f37dc7fecbfb6baeaaa","tid":1980684,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ab2969616a2789857ff061d3906ef9c94fd2e75","tid":1980684,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b58fe439c97c25f871428b1020239dbf01244c04","tid":1980684,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T08:54:39.000Z","msg":"Ok bye"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T08:59:44.000Z","msg":"55"